55+ Resort Style Living in Ormond Beach!
Located in Ormond Beach, Florida, The Falls is an active, age-restricted manufactured home community that features almost 600  home lots and a number of luxurious amenities our residents love. The manufactured homes located within this 141-acre community are nestled into the lush foliage that surrounds the community, which allows for ample privacy. Our community is beautiful with oversized lots, well-kept yards and streets, and a quiet, yet active place for our residents to call home.
This beautiful  community is full of both year-round and “snow bird” residents, which makes this the perfect Florida retirement community!
